-- Phil Jackson to Return as Los Angeles Lakers' Coach for One More Season
-- Erik Matuszewski
-- 2010-07-01T21:12:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-01/phil-jackson-to-return-as-los-angeles-lakers-coach-for-one-more-season.html

          
          
             Phil Jackson  says he’ll return for
one more season as coach of the Los Angeles Lakers.  
 Jackson, who won his record 11th National Basketball
Association championship with the Lakers this past season, said
in a statement released today by the team that the 2010-11
campaign will be his “last stand.”  
